videos.title: Welcome to Locia Farms - A Peaceful Family Farm in Ocala, Florida
videos.description:
Welcome to Locia Farms - a peaceful six-acre hideaway in Morriston, Ocala, Florida.

Welcome to Locia Farms, nestled in the heart of Morriston, Florida. Here on our six-acre family farm, we're committed to living out our faith through careful stewardship of the land and a deep sense of community.

Our happy hens roam freely, enjoying the sunshine and fresh air. They provide us with the most delicious, farm-fresh eggs you can imagine!

Video Summary:

• A Sanctuary of Life
  Welcome to Locia Farms, nestled in the heart of Morriston, Florida

• Free-Range Feathered Friends
  Our happy hens roam freely, enjoying the sunshine and fresh air

• Gathering of Chickens
  These chickens aren't just livestock; they're a part of our family

• Pecking Order
  We take pride in raising our chickens in a natural and healthy environment

• Curious Goat Close-Up
  Meet some of our playful goats! They're always up to something, bringing joy and laughter to our days

• Goat in the Grass
  These friendly goats are more than just adorable; they help us manage the land naturally

• Herd of Goats
